org.modelio.api.module.lifecycle

Class DefaultModuleLifeCycleHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.api.module.lifecycle.DefaultModuleLifeCycleHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModuleLifeCycleHandler

    public class DefaultModuleLifeCycleHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements IModuleLifeCycleHandler
    Default implementation of the IModuleLifeCycleHandler interface.

    This default implementation may be inherited by the module developers in order to simplify the code writing of the mdac session.

    Since:
    3.5
